Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符...伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被气功打伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一定时间才会现出威力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是个非常厉害的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的被打中的话 会当场没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符 你到底遇到谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是董卓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在前一届的大斗士大会的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师传授给董卓的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董卓 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 又做了些多余的事了 那个大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决胜就下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大意 威力还没过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样托下去的话 我的期待就没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是于吉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一般的斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拾壹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:02:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这是什么阿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三国史上 孙策受到重袭 死于壮年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伯符中潜藏着的是非常强烈的孙策的斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是纯粹为了战斗的龙之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了不想屈服于命运 才拜托我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我力量不足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这不是你的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的责任都在于我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初 是和吕蒙战斗时出现的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那天 发现在伯符里潜藏的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿是命名为 孙策的斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不终日而战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也不想就屈服于命运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 伯母来这之前都没有发现伯符的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 我写了一封信给张紘老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道有没有救伯符的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张紘老师的回答是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待一个名叫于吉的斗士来找伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史上 孙策是被于吉诅咒死的阿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于伯符来说 于吉是最难对付的斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张紘老师说我摆脱命运 是我的愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:05:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我所做的只会让伯符的生命消失得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从结果来看 好像被董卓发现而得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是于吉在意的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大意 威力还没过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符就这样醒不过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不起来的话 就不让你吃晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 起来 我起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会睡在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才作了一个很奇怪的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一条很大的蛇包围的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条蛇弯弯曲曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:05:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董卓大人叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么贾诩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有看穿你的想法的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华雄...你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您回来了阿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇见南阳的小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遇到孙策伯符了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个有趣的女孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不怕陌生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢 于是就没杀她 让她现出了真正的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小声地告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布什么时候会过来都不知道 这个时候你在想什么阿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾诩 脱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候变得用这种口吻来和我说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是担心董卓大人的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布好像来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李催被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不报告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道董卓大人已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐就失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:07:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人接吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想告诉他昨天的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去学校里找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符阿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿 起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 现在几点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11点多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11点 迟到很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不叫我起来阿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾说今天就让你休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心什么 怎么担心阿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是在游泳池边昏倒了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没人接 今天乐就也没来学校阿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 周瑜公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次对不起了阿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是勅令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 而且是我们找你麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去女人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在大斗士大会之后再做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为四天王不能不奉还呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样阿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈 话说回来 你有看见乐就吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐就在袁术那里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在袁术那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说起来 乐就是说要当面谈谈什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袁术的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袁术的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说阿 还是通知一下吕蒙比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是四天王嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用非要一起 总会见面的阿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是说过除四天王以外的都不要见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方阿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是蒸汽房 现在被空置着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个空房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袁术在那里 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周瑜公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊 但是现在去学校也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对巨大的垃圾没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果觉得没事做的话 能不能帮我打扫一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来拉 所以说还是在学校打架比较爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 首先是公瑾的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是 比起昨天...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张紘老师在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 为什么公瑾的房间总是那么干净
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从哪里打扫起好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三国人名辞典
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天 三天之内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈带我去见袁术了 周瑜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈 到底想...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 不是在好好干了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董卓 那个西瓜男
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是个大好人阿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向张紘老师确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你中的是董卓的朱砂掌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像很严重似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个斑纹还在蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那气功的威力会像蛇一样钻进身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直指你的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张紘说会在三天内就到达心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够救你的就只有出招的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么答案只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾打电话说不要出门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是等和公瑾联络了之后再...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 只是我的个人问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于吉 在和小于了断之前我是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 看过...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想联系他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱砂掌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一条很大的蛇包围的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该能追上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了的于吉 去洛阳找董卓的伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着公瑾行踪不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张紘老师这将会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要偷玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想作为给吕布大人的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有一点点力量也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:16:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想让吕布大人取得天下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我是不会开心的阿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这样的话 我会觉得很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是个笨蛋阿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说完话后有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我睡一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么你先走了阿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样太奇怪了阿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 你不会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也马上就会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾发来的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被左慈带走 去见袁术了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有点担心 就去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈 就是那个奇怪的卖内衣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袁术 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所打的电话不在服务区
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有相信左慈了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 袁术是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袁术是我们南阳的首领
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首领
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样阿 有听说过阿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 都到这个时候了 为什么袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是南阳阿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找董卓有事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会说好的 让你们通过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点 就是拼命了也要通过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这样的话只有一起上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了阿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进 这里是我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:18:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了的西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃多少都可以 请随便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是西瓜的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 破了以后全是红的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人的头一样阿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是什么人阿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把伯符的朱砂掌解开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么阿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗士的打斗难道是孩子的打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激烈的运动会加速蛇的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的乱斗奏效了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想让你见的女人 想让你杀了那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你来和这个女人的生命交换
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 冲着这边来的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是 周瑜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么阿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南阳学院的首领袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被一个死人操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那么勅令呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 没有死的是甘宁的问题阿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈元放 这家伙就是袁术的真身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈把袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边都不是阿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是王允 王允子师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王允子师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在董卓的暗黑时代 是董卓的义弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吕布奉先笼络 让她杀害董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是开创三国时代的中心人物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野心的政治家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐就
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们被绑的这段期间里发生了不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样被绑着也不坏阿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被绑着也不坏 你果然有这个兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比较天真阿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐就 请振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 西瓜大战 夏天来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.48,0:23:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也 被打倒了
